{
  "stem": "5470.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But don't let the Germans know who are walking still around the camp what's going on inside-- inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I can't control if they are coming in and doing some harm to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, uh, that's where they said to me-- there was a question asked, what can we do on the-- keep the-- that's what I said.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Keep the whole organization going as it is as much as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we have to eat, and all these things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, yes, but what's going to happen if it takes longer?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And can we then keep our Sabbath?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who wants to keep the Sabbath, they can keep the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I expect that if they are keeping the Sabbath, that they will [? give ?] their, uh, help on the Sunday that all-- everybody can get their [? meal. ?] And just finished that sentence.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then from behind, in the hall, someone called out and said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Van As, there's telephone for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, telephone for me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The whole day, the telephone was ringing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I said, yeah, what's on?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, the Canadians arrived!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, approximately 1,000 people by the time in the hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they got to know at once that the Canadians were there, so they jumped out of the windows!",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they walked over to the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my wife was just walking outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was nearly toppled over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was quite pregnant at the time from our son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they ran out towards the farm, and that's where they were picked up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the, uh, commander-- that was Captain Morrison-- came to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we together went to the office where-- where-- the office of Gemmecker was before.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
